# 🚍 Public Routes Management System

This Folder serves as a centralized system to manage all public transportation routes efficiently.

## 📌 Overview

The application provides a structured and scalable way to store, manage, and access public route data. It ensures consistency across the system and simplifies updates and maintenance.

## ⚙️ Features

- 📍 Centralized route management  
- 🗺️ Organized and structured route data  
- ⚡ Fast and optimized performance with Next.js  
- 🔄 Easy updates and maintainability  
- 📊 Scalable architecture for future enhancements  

## 🧱 Architecture

- Built with **Next.js** for server-side rendering and performance  
- Modular structure for better maintainability  
- API routes used for handling backend logic  
- Separation of concerns between data, services, and UI  


## 🛠️ Core Concept

All public routes are managed in a centralized layer, making it easy to:

- Add new routes  
- Update existing routes  
- Maintain consistency across the platform  
- Integrate with other services or APIs  

## 🔮 Future Scope

- Real-time route updates  
- Integration with maps and geolocation services  
- Admin dashboard for route management  
- Analytics and reporting features  

